  Also check out OpenBTS [1], Serval [2], and the work that Rhizomatica
is doing in Mexico[3].  There are some decent options out there for
running a local GSM network -- the tricky part comes when you want to
connect to the larger telephone network....

  Osmocom is pretty cool to play around with, not to mention that
catcher catcher is only compatible with OsmocomBB[4] (an interesting
research opportunity for 30c3 if ever there was one...)

~Griffin

